  "slug": "easiest-ever-slow-cooker-lasagna",
  "title": "Easiest Ever Slow Cooker Lasagna",
  "subtitle": "The kind of dinner that cooks itself.",
  "excerpt": "Easiest Ever Slow Cooker Lasagna. A slow-cooker dish that does its own work, set it in the morning, serve it at dinner.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "From Rebecca's personal cookbook, a recipe she's made many times in her own kitchen.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Easiest Ever Slow Cooker Lasagna. A British home-cook's dish, the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "It runs in the slow cooker so the work is at the start of the day and the dinner cooks itself.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
